    <p><em><%= @business.opening_hours %></em></p>
    <p><em><%= @business.telephone %></em></p>
    <p><em><%= @business.email %></em></p>
    <a><em><%= @business.website_url %></em></a>
    </div>

    </div>
    This is commented out for the demo on friday since the tabs are not yet functional:
    All of the code above will move to the Contact tab eventually.
    -->
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


